'''Debora Patta''' (* 13. julija [[1964]]<ref>[http://w11.zetaboards.com/White_House/profile/3599886/ Perfil de Debora Patta]</ref>, [[Simbabwe|Zimbabwe]]) jo nimska žurnalistka, kótaraž jo była wót 1984 do 1990 šefredaktorka nimskich nowinow Radio702<ref>[http://www.radioemiliaromagna.it/eventi/premio_globo_tricolore.aspx ''La giornalista investigativa più famosa in Sudafrica, di origine calabrese ma nata in Zimbabwe, Debora Patta'']</ref><ref>[http://www.mediaclubsouthafrica.com/index.php?option=com_content&view=article&id=1999:patta-121010&catid=49:medianews&Itemid=113 '''La vita' looks 'bella' for Debora Patta'']</ref><ref name="Segar">{{Pśedłoga:Cite news|last = Segar|first = Sue|title = Interview with Debora Patta: Not all Glamour|url = http://www.witness.co.za/index.php?showcontent&global%5B_id%5D=8363|accessdate = 2 março 2013|newspaper = The Witness|date = 30 May 2008}}</ref>, wót 1990 do 1998 šefredaktorka nimskich nowinow e.tv.

